<!-- review-gate:begin -->
# Review Gate (mandatory before commit/push)
Before any `git commit` (or `git push`), follow `.review-gate/GATE.md`:
1. Review the diff using `.review-gate/agents/` + `.review-gate/skills/` as checklists.
2. Fix every real finding.
3. Run: bash .review-gate/review-gate.sh attest --ran review,clean-code   (add test/docs if changed)
4. Then commit/push.
A git hook blocks the action until attest passes. Honesty gate — never bypass with --no-verify.
Verify commands: .review-gate/gate.config.json
<!-- review-gate:end -->
